    <string name="privacy_content">Welcome to this application (hereinafter referred to as "the App"). We value the protection of your personal information. Please read the following to understand how we collect and use information:\n\n【1. Information Collected】\n- Device information (such as model, system version, etc.)\n- Usage data (such as launch count, crash information, etc.)\n\n【2. Information Usage】\n- To optimize product and service experience\n- For data analysis and troubleshooting\n- To comply with relevant laws and regulations\n\n【3. Information Protection】\nWe will take reasonable measures to ensure information security and prevent leakage, loss, or illegal access.\n\n【4. Your Rights】\n- You have the right to choose whether to agree to this policy\n- You can stop using this App at any time\n- If you have any questions, please contact us at any time\n\n【5. Policy Updates】\nWe may update the privacy policy from time to time, and changes will be notified in the App.</string>
